<subSubSection id="94638C0C9A7950E427A4718E841FDFC3" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="holotype">
<paragraph id="5E01D18A09718088E7E7F467A494671D" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Holotype.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B4A3FD14C5A3F98B983CC85FE3055CD4" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
BRAZIL. Minas Gerais, Estrada Conselheiro Mata, a 2 km do asfalto, Diamantina, 11 April 1982, 
<emphasis id="C666F4BFE3BD80F86C52B3AA48D9491C" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">L. Rossi, A. Furlan, N.L. Menezes, N. Hensold, H.L. Wagner &amp; E.M. Isejima 3317</emphasis>
